dt <- read_csv("/Users/placenameday/R study/edf_demo/data/processed/eye_tacking/ea/data/raw_time_b3_sas_ps.gz") %>%
  mutate(Target=case_when(sas_g=="high"~"HPA",
                          sas_g=="low"~"LPA"),
         AOI=case_when(AOI=="b3_ne"~"neutral",
                       AOI=="b3_neg"~"dysphoric",
                       AOI=="b3_pos"~"positive",
                       AOI=="b3_thr"~"threat")) %>%
  filter(sas_g != "mid") %>% rename(Time=time_bin)


ggplot(dt, aes(x=Time, y=ps, color=AOI)) +
  facet_grid(rows = vars(Target)) +
  stat_summary(fun.y=mean, geom="point")

nk <- read_csv("/Users/placenameday/R study/edf_demo/data/processed/eye_tacking/ea/data/b3_timec_pwc_sas_a_ps.csv")


nk2 <- nk  %>% select(Target, Time, neutral, positive, dysphoric, threat) %>%
  distinct() %>% pivot_longer(3:6, names_to = "AOI", values_to = "Dominance_Times")

timezone <- nk %>% group_by(Time) %>%
  summarise(pairsn = n())

timezone$inter <- append(diff(timezone$Time),0)

t <- timezone %>% filter(inter>1500)
t
## # A tibble: 4  3
##    Time pairsn inter
##   <dbl>  <int> <dbl>
## 1  4000      2  1900
## 2  7400      1  2400
## 3 10000      1  3100
## 4 22100      1  2300
nt <- t$Time/1000

dt_v2 <- full_join(dt, nk2) %>% mutate(Time=Time/1000, AOI=factor(AOI, levels=c("threat",  "dysphoric", "positive", "neutral")))
dt_v <- dt_v2 %>%
  mutate(Dominance_Times=factor(Dominance_Times, levels=c(0,1,2,3)))

dt_rank <- dt_v2 %>% mutate(AOI=factor(AOI, levels=c("neutral", "positive", "dysphoric", "threat"))) %>%
  group_by(Target, Time, AOI) %>%
  mutate(Dominance_Times=as.numeric(Dominance_Times)) %>%
  summarise(Dominance_Times=mean(Dominance_Times, na.rm=T))

p3 <- ggplot(dt_rank, aes(x=Time, y=AOI, fill=Dominance_Times)) +
  facet_grid(rows = vars(Target)) +
  geom_raster() + scale_fill_viridis() +
  theme_tufte(base_family="Helvetica") +
  guides(fill=guide_legend(title="DCPC")) +
  labs(y="Stimuli") +
  theme(axis.ticks=element_blank(),
        legend.title=element_text(face = "bold"),
        strip.text.y=element_text(face = "bold"),
        legend.key.size = unit(0.4, 'cm'),
        axis.text.x=element_blank(),axis.title.x=element_blank(),
        axis.text.y=element_blank(),
        legend.text=element_text(face = "bold"),
        axis.title.y=element_text(face = "bold"),
        plot.margin=unit(c(1,1,0,1), "cm"))

p4 <- ggplot(dt_v, aes(x=Time, y=ps, color=AOI)) +
  facet_grid(rows = vars(Target)) +
  stat_summary(fun.y=mean, geom="line", size=1, alpha = 0.75) +
  geom_vline(xintercept = nt,linetype="dotted", 
                color = "black", size=1, alpha = 0.55) +
  theme(legend.key.size = unit(5, "pt"), legend.position = "right", legend.key.width = unit(15, "pt"), legend.title=element_text(face = "bold"), axis.title.x=element_text(face = "bold"),
        axis.title.y=element_text(face = "bold"),
        axis.text.x=element_text(face = "bold"),
        axis.text.y=element_text(face = "bold"),
        strip.text.y=element_text(face = "bold"),
        legend.text=element_text(face = "bold"),
        plot.margin=unit(c(0,1,1,1), "cm")) +
  labs(colour = "Stimuli") +
  labs(y="Gaze proportion") +
  labs(x="Time(s)")+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = append(nt, c(0,30)))

p3_npg = p3
p4_npg = p4 + ggsci::scale_color_npg()

fig2 <- plot_grid(p3, p4_npg, ncol = 1, align = "v",rel_heights = c(1, 2), labels = c("A", "B"))

fig2
